*Usage note: ''This masculine word is irregular. '''Људи''' (people, men) is the plural form of the singular word '''човек''' (man).  Because of the existence of dual grammatical numbers in Serbian, the dual form (the form for 2, 3, and 4) is '''човека'''.  The dual numbers also apply to any higher numbers ending in 2, 3, and 4, such as 22, 23, and 24.''
*:Example of dual numbers:  ''Два човека су ишла цестом.'' (''Two men walked down the street.'')
*:Example of plural:  ''Пет људи су ишли цестом.'' (''Five men/people walked down the street.'')
